description.en:
Intercrone is a digital peer-to-peer currency with a self-regulated financial system.

A decentralized system based on the proof of stake, where all transactions can be viewed in a public explorer. This means that no one has the sole control and everything is transparent to everyone on the network.

The transactions are verified by network nodes and recorded in a publicly distributed general Ledger called Blockchain.

With Intercrone you can transfer money to other people not using service provider in between.
